MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the DG9 area of Stranraer, affecting properties in Bridge of Aldouran and surrounding areas. It has been necessary for our engineers to carry out an emergency shutdown at 10:36am due to reports of a grounded overhead line near Kathleen Cottage and this may affect the supply to your property. We will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 12:45pm. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 10:38am on Sunday, 13 December 2020
